lyrics_raw: [Verse 1] / I was a liar, I gave into the fire / I know I should’ve fought it / At least I’m being honest / Feel like a failure, cause I know that I failed you / I should’ve done you better cause you don’t want a liar / [Pre-Chorus] / And I know, and I know, and I know she gives you everything / But boy, I couldn’t give it to you / And I know, and I know, and I know that you got everything / But I got nothing here without you / [Chorus] / So one last time / I need to be the one who takes you home / One more time / I promise after that, I’ll let you go / Baby, I don’t care if you got her in your heart / All I really care is you wake up in my arms / One last time / I need to be the one who takes you home / [Verse 2] / I don’t deserve it / I know I don’t deserve it / But stay with me a minute, I’ll swear I’ll make it worth it / Can’t you forgive me? / At least just temporarily / I know that this is my fault, I should have been more careful / [Pre-Chorus] / And I know, and I know, and I know she gives you everything / But boy, I couldn’t give it to you / And I know, and I know, and I know that you got everything / But I got nothing here without you, baby / [Chorus] / So one last time / I need to be the one who takes you home / One more time / I promise after that, I’ll let you go / Baby, I don’t care if you got her in your heart / All I really care is you wake up in my arms / One last time / I need to be the one who takes you home / [Bridge] / I know I should've fought it, at least I'm being honest / Just stay with me a minute, I swear I’ll make it worth it / Cause I don’t want to be without you / [Chorus] / So one last time / I need to be the one who takes you home / One more time / I promise after that, I’ll let you go / Baby, I don’t care if you got her in your heart / All I really care is you wake up in my arms / One last time / I need to be the one who takes you home / [Outro] / One last time / I need to be the one who takes you home
